To set up static IP addresses on RECUV_VICON:
1. In any web browser type: 192.168.20.0
2. Enter password to RECUV_VICON
3. Find MAC address corresponding to desired device
4. From Network address dropdown select DHCP/static routes
5. From static IP section select Create New
6. Insert desired name, MAC address for desired device, and custom IP address
7. Click "Save and Apply"
8  Reconnect device to RECUV_VICON to update assigned IP address
 
